remixlab.bias.branch

Class Profile<E extends Enum<E>,K extends Shortcut,A extends Action<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • remixlab.bias.branch.Profile<E,K,A>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - User-defined Action.
    E - 'Reference' enum action set, used to parameterize the user-defined action.
    K - Shortcut
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Copyable

    public class Profile<E extends Enum<E>,K extends Shortcut,A extends Action<E>>
extends Object
implements Copyable
    A mapping defining Shortcut to Action bindings, implemented as a parameterized hash-map wrap. Profiles are internally used by Branches to parse BogusEvents into GenericGrabber object Actions.
